# Sukabumi 30-minute duty cycle
#
# 25 min ON / 5 min OFF — captures every 30 minutes (48/day)
#
# Use this schedule to conserve battery during low-solar periods
# or when less frequent monitoring is acceptable.
#
# ORC-OS handles shutdown, typically within ~3 minutes. The 25-min
# ON window is a generous backstop. Witty Pi forces shutdown at
# minute 25 if ORC-OS hasn't, leaving a 5-min buffer before next wake.

BEGIN 2026-01-01 00:00:00
END   2099-12-31 23:59:59
ON    M25
OFF   M5
